HEADWORD: cold-heartedness
<hw>cold"-heart`ed*ness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an absence of concern
for the welfare of others; indifference to the suffering of
others.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> heartlessness, hardheartedness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

